name: SupplyDelivery
title: SupplyDelivery
publisher: Health Level Seven International (Orders and Observations)
description: Record of delivery of what was requested/ordered and provides evidence of delivery.

elements.name: SupplyDelivery
elements.description: Record of delivery of what was requested/ordered and provides evidence of delivery.

elements.name: identifier
elements.description: Identifier for the supply delivery event that is used to identify it across multiple disparate systems.

elements.name: basedOn
elements.description: A plan, proposal or order that is fulfilled in whole or in part by this delivery.

elements.name: partOf
elements.description: A larger event of which this particular event is a component or step.

elements.name: status
elements.description: A code specifying the state of the delivery.

elements.name: patient
elements.description: A link to a resource representing the person whom the delivered item is for.

elements.name: type
elements.description: Indicates the type of dispensing event that is performed.

elements.name: suppliedItem
elements.description: The item that is being delivered or has been supplied.

elements.name: occurrenceDateTime
elements.description: The date or time(s) the activity occurred.

elements.name: occurrencePeriod
elements.description: The date or time(s) the activity occurred.

elements.name: occurrenceTiming
elements.description: The date or time(s) the activity occurred.

elements.name: supplier
elements.description: The individual responsible for dispensing the medication, supplier or device.

elements.name: destination
elements.description: Identification of the facility/location where the Supply was shipped to, as part of the dispense event.

elements.name: receiver
elements.description: Identifies the person who picked up the Supply.
